/******************************************************************************
 * Another JT Arpeggiator
 *
 * A dedicated trance arpeggiator and bass sequencer for the Behringer JT-4000M.
 *
 * Features
 * --------
 * - Trance arpeggiator
 * - Bass sequencer
 * - MIDI clock (Internal / External)
 * - MIDI CC automation
 * - Performance page with LFO
 *
 * Hardware
 * --------
 * - Arduino Nano
 * - 6 Buttons
 * - 6 LEDs
 * - 4 Pots
 * - MIDI IN
 * - MIDI OUT
 *
 * Version : 0.1
 ******************************************************************************/

//=============================================================================
// Project Goal
//=============================================================================
//
// Create a dedicated trance arpeggiator and performance controller
// for the Behringer JT-4000M.
//
// The instrument should inspire musical ideas immediately,
// while remaining simple enough to operate without a manual.
//
// The focus is not feature count.
// The focus is musicality.
//

 //=============================================================================
// Roadmap
//=============================================================================
//
// [x] Project structure
