// [ ] Arp engine
// [ ] Bass engine
// [ ] Live engine
// [ ] Preset storage
//

//=============================================================================
// Design Rules
//=============================================================================
//
// - Keep it musical before technical.
// - Avoid random generators.
// - Prefer deterministic patterns.
// - The arp creates interest.
// - The bass creates groove.
// - Live page creates emotion.
// - Manual control always has priority.
// - Keep the interface simple.
// - Version 1 before Version 2.
//

